options.text: Can you tell me about your cape?

450d3dba-ca8c-4970-a16d-7e3a39b6540b.text:
Certainly! Skillcapes are a symbol of achievement. Only
people who have mastered a skill and reached level 99
can get their hands on them and gain the benefits they
carry.

ac598b2c-55c4-4b0a-af97-f6ab050ca8a0.text:

to quickly look over this, and then talk to me again.

fced1505-3759-4ae4-b3f3-b87e421faafd.text:

research notes. I notice that you brought the head
wizard a special talisman that was the key to our finally
unlocking the puzzle.

fff4dfe3-bf1c-4f9f-b7de-187cdefcb77b.text:

regarding the Rune Essence, I think we have finally
unlocked the power to

the Wizards' Tower. I trust his judgement on whether
to let you in on our little secret or not.
